HEADWORD: Hectostere
<hw>Hec"to*stere</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>hectost⟦egrave⟧re</ets>; Gr. <?/ hundred + F.
<ets>st⟦egrave⟧re</ets>.]</ety> <def>A measure of solidity, containing
